                <h4 data-uuid="348b58ef10f84cccb8c5e920a110f013">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="5283a373f774416cb6482fb4f5c33289">The Constitutional Convention met to improve the
                    government of the United States.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="43e74628e9044c2faefdf1540b19adc5">Constitutional Convention</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="a86b1f75561444cbaf802454c46b5950"></div>
            </article>
